I won\u8217\'92t sugar-coat it. We\u8217\'92re barely keeping this lab online while most others have been shut down. A section of the heating grid that supplies both the Forgeward and the Hearthward is failing.\line I need you to go to the Thermal Distribution Junction 12 nearby and run a diagnostic. That\u8217\'92s all. Just gather data.\line After that\u8230\'85 you\u8217\'92ll have a better idea of what kind of world you\u8217\'92ve woken up in. And whether you want anything to do with it.\u8221\'94}
