Yes \u8212\'97 let's finally build Calethina\u8217\'92s personal questline.This is one of the most important optional threads in the game. It should feel meaningful, emotionally resonant, and deeply educational about the world of Tepenia without ever feeling mandatory. The player should come away understanding far more about the Long Night War, the evacuation, the Falkland Treaty, Bridge Units, and the true state of Concordia than they would from the main story alone.Here\u8217\'92s a strong, flexible structure for her questline:Questline Title: \u8220\'93Echoes of the Bridge\u8221\'94 (or \u8220\'93Fading Signal\u8221\'94)Overall Arc: Calethina is slowly degrading. As the player helps diagnose and stabilize her, they uncover layers of hidden history, suppressed truths, and the personal cost of survival in post-war Tepenia.}
